{"title":"节奏和火焰","authors":["阿戈斯提纽·内托"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":2,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"节奏和火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔安哥拉〕阿戈斯提纽·内托"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……街上叮当的铁链声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林子的绿荫里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……婉啭的鸟语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和着棕榈树的轻微的旋律。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一人高的野草里的火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在低矮的茅房上的火焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在望不到头的路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走着千百万人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们被士兵从各处赶到这些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望不到头的路上来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路伸展到远方，目光看不到的地方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疲乏的、搭拉着胳膊的人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越来越多地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这些望不到头的路上经过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞蹈和鼓声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"色彩和光的节奏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓声和行动的节奏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破碎的脚的步履的节奏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渗透沙土的血的节奏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是节奏——不停的节奏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淌着血的战斗着的非洲的节奏声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（韩世钟译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}